    "biography": {
      "value": "<p><em>The ground ripples and tears as rocks fall, jets of flame erupt, and howling winds rage around a rocky creature.</em><br><em><strong>Spirit of the Land.</strong></em> Elemental loci are living spirits inhabiting or embodying tracts of land and geographical features. They are the ultimate personification of nature—the land itself come to life. They vary in size from small hills to entire ridge lines, with no discernible pattern to where they take root.<br><em><strong>Stubborn Nature.</strong></em> Elemental loci are fiercely protective of their chosen location. They tolerate no interference in the natural order and challenge all who despoil the land, be they mortal, monster, or god.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl-bf.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}"
    }
